{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"697f125e-af93-429d-ac2b-106cf13717ef","content":"In MSTest v4, the `TestMethodAttribute(string)` constructor's string parameter became a `[CallerMemberName]` parameter, so passing a display name positionally no longer sets the display name — it interferes with caller info.\n\n**Fix:** Use the named `DisplayName` property instead:\n\n```csharp\n// Before (v3):  [TestMethod(\"my name\")]\n// After  (v4):  [TestMethod(DisplayName = \"my name\")]\n```\n\nApplying the fix now:","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01B5cfBEz5TjJ6y28RFEjehV","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Updating TestMethod attributes"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01JmPD21zRqF5AVTsXTeqUj1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-75cd2f0abe6240e0856ab0b125c69955/AuthTests.cs","old_str":"    [TestMethod(\"Verify user login works correctly\")]","new_str":"    [TestMethod(DisplayName = \"Verify user login works correctly\")]"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"edit the file at /tmp/sv-75cd2f0abe6240e0856ab0b125c69955/AuthTests.cs."},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01AGWRJg4BYpZRmXPmDcDgqi","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-75cd2f0abe6240e0856ab0b125c69955/AuthTests.cs","old_str":"    [TestMethodAttribute(\"Check admin privileges are enforced\")]","new_str":"    [TestMethod(DisplayName = \"Check admin privileges are enforced\")]"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"edit the file at /tmp/sv-75cd2f0abe6240e0856ab0b125c69955/AuthTests.cs."},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_0149cmoEiNnSTPq9ohEe35DS","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-75cd2f0abe6240e0856ab0b125c69955/AuthTests.cs","old_str":"    [TestMethod(\"Ensure logout clears session\")]","new_str":"    [TestMethod(DisplayName = \"Ensure logout clears session\")]"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"edit the file at /tmp/sv-75cd2f0abe6240e0856ab0b125c69955/AuthTests.cs."}],"interactionId":"5d0ff9f3-32a1-49af-bdd5-196dd0a61bc6","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningTe